piece of a conversation

00:44:50.574 --> 00:44:51.740
with other people with that.

00:44:51.740 --> 00:44:56.262
And they were having an argument
about that, back and forth.

00:44:56.262 --> 00:44:57.720
Both the people
were very informed,

00:44:57.720 --> 00:45:00.460
so I don't know who
to believe on it.

00:45:00.460 --> 00:45:02.300
What are his objectives?

00:45:02.300 --> 00:45:04.450
Probably all of
Ukraine, a lot of people

00:45:04.450 --> 00:45:08.800
would say-- at least
the parts of the Ukraine

00:45:08.800 --> 00:45:11.970
that would allow him a
land bridge to the Crimea

00:45:11.970 --> 00:45:15.420
and connect to Moldava-- that's
another opinion that I've

00:45:15.420 --> 00:45:17.240
heard.

00:45:17.240 --> 00:45:21.540
Another opinion
that I've heard is

00:45:21.540 --> 00:45:23.800
that not only
Ukraine, but Belarus.

00:45:23.800 --> 00:45:26.810
Ukraine's the first
step in Belarus.

00:45:26.810 --> 00:45:30.819
And also there's a lot
of fear, apparently--

00:45:30.819 --> 00:45:32.860
