00:45:32.860 --> 00:45:36.000
not the government--
there's a lot

00:45:36.000 --> 00:45:40.200
of fear among prominent figures
in the Baltic states about what

00:45:40.200 --> 00:45:43.414
might be-- the big cyber-attack
they launched in the Estonians

00:45:43.414 --> 00:45:44.955
a couple years ago
and the kidnapping

00:45:44.955 --> 00:45:47.022
of the Estonian officer.

00:45:47.022 --> 00:45:49.230
And there's been a shifting
of all the Polish defense

00:45:49.230 --> 00:45:50.220
forces around.

00:45:50.220 --> 00:45:52.550
But basically, to look on
the border with Ukraine.

00:45:52.550 --> 00:45:56.040
But I don't know what he wants.

00:45:56.040 --> 00:45:58.610
I'm not a Russian
expert, by far.

